1. Moj *brat* je danas imao rođendan. (My *brother* had his birthday today.)
2. *Bratom* sam se družio celo popodne. (I hung out with my *brother* all afternoon.)
3. *Brat* mi je najbolji prijatelj. (My *brother* is my best friend.)
4. Bio sam *bratom* svojoj sestri kada joj je bilo teško. (I was like a *brother* to my sister when she was going through a hard time.)
5. Ne bih bio ovde da nije mog *brata*. (I wouldn't be here if it weren't for my *brother*.)
6. *Bratu* sam dao novac da plati račune. (I gave money to my *brother* to pay the bills.)
7. Imam tri *brata* i jednu sestru. (I have three *brothers* and one sister.)
8. *Brata* nisam video od prošle godine. (I haven't seen my *brother* since last year.)
9. *Bratstvo* je veoma važno u našoj kulturi. (*Brotherhood* is very important in our culture.)
10. *Bratski* odnos između dva naroda može da dovede do mirnog rešenja. (*Brotherly* relations between two nations can lead to peaceful resolution.)